  "title": "Lead - Talent Acquisition (IT, Technical) / Talent Management (Information Technology)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Lead - Talent Acquisition (IT, Technical) / Talent Management (Information Technology)</strong></p><p>Work with the Hiring Leaders to handle IT, Technical roles for the South East Asia Region including Singapore. <br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore</p><ul><li><strong>End to End IT, Technical Recruitment: Partners with the Sales and Business Function Hiring Leaders to identify, source, and manage the end-to-end hiring activities. </strong></li><li><strong>Planning and hiring includes Information Technology positions that covers Cybersecurity, Infrastructure, Cloud, Network, Solution Enterprises roles.</strong></li><li>Involved in competitive activities in the region/ hiring track, determines hiring potential from key universities within the region in to order to develop the staffing plan to meet requirements of the units/ region.</li><li>Involved in career fairs, pre-placement presentations, vendor conferences, etc.), Develops and implements round-the-year engagement initiatives with key stakeholders in the region.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong knowledge of Information Technology such as Artificial Intelligence, Enterprise Solutions, Cybersecurity, Infrastructure, Cloud Platform, Network and Software.</strong></li><li>Proven track record in IT/ Technical recruitment within an in-house portfolio or Agency, preferably within a similar industry.</li><li>Strong experience in IT / Technical end-to-end recruitment.</li><li>Recruitment experience across Sales hiring will be key to have.</li><li>Strong sourcing strategy experience including proactive sourcing</li><li>Experienced with senior level stakeholder management and managing difficult conversations</li></ul><p><br />We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p><br />Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to :jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p><br /><br />Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
